In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} year whose final digit is 2 or 7 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} are {{ill|Ren|ja|壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} or {{ill|Tei|ja|丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}), the month of {{ill|November|ja|11月|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|lt=Month|lt_ja=月|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of {{ill|Jinshi|ja|壬子|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (from {{ill|Heavy Snow|ja|大雪|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} until the day before {{ill|Lesser Cold|ja|小寒|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) as applicable.

==Yang Water Rat (壬子)'s Days==
==={{nihongo|selection days|選日|senjitsu}}===
The selected day for {{ill|Jinshi|ja|壬子|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} is the 1st day of {{ill|Hassen|ja|八専|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.

