It is the 49th combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, preceded by {{ill|Xinhai|ja|辛亥|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and followed by {{ill|Guichuu|ja|癸丑|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. In the context of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|陰陽五行思想|lt=Yin Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=陰陽五行|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} symbol {{ill|Ren|ja|壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Water|ja|水|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} symbol {{ill|Rat|ja|子 (十二支)|lt=Rat|lt_ja=子|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Water|ja|水|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, resulting in a harmonious relationship ({{ill|Hiwa|ja|比和|1=Wuxing (Chinese philosophy)#Harmonious Relationship (比和)|2=ja|3=五行思想#比和（ひわ）|lt=Harmonious Relationship (Five Elements)|4=el|5=Ου Σιν|lt=Hiwa|lt_ja=比和|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}).  
==Yang Water Rat (壬子)'s Years==
A year in the {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} that leaves a remainder of 52 when divided by 60 is a {{ill|year|ja|年|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} of {{ill|Jinshi|ja|壬子|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
