It is the 49th combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, preceded by {{ill|Xinhai|ja|辛亥|qq=draft|qq=draft}} and followed by {{ill|Guichuu|ja|癸丑|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. In the context of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|陰陽五行思想|lt=Yin Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=陰陽五行|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft}} symbol {{ill|Ren|ja|壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Water|ja|水|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, while the {{ill|Earthly Branches|ja|十二支|qq=draft|qq=draft}} symbol {{ill|Rat|ja|子 (十二支)|lt=Rat|lt_ja=子|qq=draft|qq=draft}} represents yang {{ill|Water|ja|水|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, resulting in a harmonious relationship ({{ill|Hiwa|ja|比和|1=Wuxing (Chinese philosophy)#Harmonious Relationship (比和)|2=ja|3=五行思想#比和（ひわ）|1=比和|1=Wuxing (Chinese philosophy)#Harmonious Relationship (比和)|2=ja|3=五行思想#比和（ひわ）|lt=Harmonious Relationship (Five Elements)|qq=Harmonious Relationship (Five Elements)|4=el|5=Ου Σιν|lt=Hiwa|lt_ja=比和|qq=draft|qq=draft}}).  
==Yang Water Rat (壬子)'s Years==
A year in the {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft}} that leaves a remainder of 52 when divided by 60 is a {{ill|year|ja|年|qq=draft|qq=draft}} of {{ill|Jinshi|ja|壬子|qq=draft|qq=draft}}.
