== Superstitions around Yang Water Rat years ==
Because the water element is duplicated, a superstition arose that while many fires occur in {{ill|Besshi|ja|丙午|qq=draft|qq=draft}} years, many water disasters ({{ill|Water disaster|ja|水害|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) occur in {{ill|Jinshi|ja|壬子|qq=draft|qq=draft}} years. In the late Edo period, {{ill|Kyokutei Bakin|ja|曲亭馬琴|qq=draft|qq=draft}} remarked, "If it is so with a Besshi year, then in a Jinshi year the double presence of water elements will surely bring about a great flood."

However, the superstition that "men born in a Jinshi year have weak constitutions" did not spread; for instance, in {{ill|1972 AD|ja|1972nd year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (Shōwa 47), nearly 2 million births occurred during a Jinshi year as part of the second {{ill|Baby Boom|ja|ベビーブーム|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, and there are no recorded instances from {{ill|1852 AD|ja|1852nd year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (Kaei 5) or {{ill|1912 AD|ja|1912nd year|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (Meiji 45/Taishō 1) of men being unable to marry due to being born in a Jinshi year.

==Yang Water Rat (壬子)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft}} year whose final digit is 2 or 7 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft}} are {{ill|Ren|ja|壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|qq=draft|qq=draft}} or {{ill|Tei|ja|丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|qq=draft|qq=draft}}), the month of {{ill|November|ja|11月|qq=draft|qq=draft}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|lt=Month|lt_ja=月|qq=draft|qq=draft}} of {{ill|Jinshi|ja|壬子|qq=draft|qq=draft}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (from {{ill|Heavy Snow|ja|大雪|qq=draft|qq=draft}} until the day before {{ill|Lesser Cold|ja|小寒|qq=draft|qq=draft}}) as applicable.

==Yang Water Rat (壬子)'s Days==
==={{nihongo|selection days|選日|senjitsu}}===
The selected day for {{ill|Jinshi|ja|壬子|qq=draft|qq=draft}} is the 1st day of {{ill|Hassen|ja|八専|qq=draft|qq=draft}}.

