A year in the {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Western calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=}} that leaves a remainder of 52 when divided by 60 is a {{ill|year|ja|年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/year|qq=}} of {{ill|Jinshi|ja|壬子|1=Yang Water Rat|2=ja|3=壬子|4=zh|5=壬子|6=ko|7=임자|lt_ko=임자|8=fr|9=Rat de eau|10=de|11=Wasser-Ratte|12=en|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Water Rat|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jinshi|qq=}}.
