== Superstitions around Yang Water Rat years ==
Because the water element is duplicated, a superstition arose that while many fires occur in {{ill|Besshi|ja|1=Yang Fire Horse|2=ja|丙午|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Besshi|qq=}} years, many water disasters ({{ill|Water disaster|ja|水害|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Water disaster|qq=}}) occur in {{ill|Jinshi|ja|壬子|1=Yang Water Rat|2=ja|3=壬子|4=zh|5=壬子|6=ko|7=임자|lt_ko=임자|8=fr|9=Rat de eau|10=de|11=Wasser-Ratte|12=en|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Water Rat|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jinshi|qq=}} years. In the late Edo period, {{ill|Kyokutei Bakin|ja|曲亭馬琴|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kyokutei Bakin|qq=}} remarked, "If it is so with a Besshi year, then in a Jinshi year the double presence of water elements will surely bring about a great flood."

However, the superstition that "men born in a Jinshi year have weak constitutions" did not spread; for instance, in {{ill|1972 AD|ja|1972nd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1972 AD|qq=}} (Shōwa 47), nearly 2 million births occurred during a Jinshi year as part of the second {{ill|Baby Boom|ja|ベビーブーム|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Baby Boom|qq=}}, and there are no recorded instances from {{ill|1852 AD|ja|1852nd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1852 AD|qq=}} (Kaei 5) or {{ill|1912 AD|ja|1912nd year|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/1912 AD|qq=}} (Meiji 45/Taishō 1) of men being unable to marry due to being born in a Jinshi year.

==Yang Water Rat (壬子)'s Months==
In a {{ill|Western calendar|ja|西暦|1=Common Era|2=ja|3=西暦|4=zh|5=公元|6=es|7=Era común|8=nl|9=Gangbare jaartelling|10=simple|11=Common Era|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Western calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Common Era|qq=}} year whose final digit is 2 or 7 (when the {{ill|Heavenly Stems|ja|十干|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavenly Stems|qq=}} are {{ill|Ren|ja|壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ren|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoe (壬)|qq=}} or {{ill|Tei|ja|丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tei|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoto (丁)|qq=}}), the month of {{ill|November|ja|11月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/November|qq=}} is designated as the {{ill|month (calendar)|ja|月 (暦)|lt=Month|lt_ja=月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/month (calendar)|qq=}} of {{ill|Jinshi|ja|壬子|1=Yang Water Rat|2=ja|3=壬子|4=zh|5=壬子|6=ko|7=임자|lt_ko=임자|8=fr|9=Rat de eau|10=de|11=Wasser-Ratte|12=en|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Water Rat|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jinshi|qq=}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the {{ill|Seasonal Month|ja|節月|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Seasonal Month|qq=}} (from {{ill|Heavy Snow|ja|大雪|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Heavy Snow|qq=}} until the day before {{ill|Lesser Cold|ja|小寒|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lesser Cold|qq=}}) as applicable.

==Yang Water Rat (壬子)'s Days==
==={{nihongo|selection days|選日|senjitsu|qq=}}===
The selected day for {{ill|Jinshi|ja|壬子|1=Yang Water Rat|2=ja|3=壬子|4=zh|5=壬子|6=ko|7=임자|lt_ko=임자|8=fr|9=Rat de eau|10=de|11=Wasser-Ratte|12=en|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Water Rat|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jinshi|qq=}} is the 1st day of {{ill|Hassen|ja|八専|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hassen|qq=}}.

