It is the 49th combination of the {{ill|Sexagenary cycle|ja|六十干支|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sexagenary cycle|qq=}}, preceded by {{ill|Xinhai|ja|1=Yin Metal Pig|2=ja|辛亥|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xinhai|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Xinhai|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Metal Pig|qq=}} and followed by {{ill|Guichuu|ja|1=Yin Water Ox|2=ja|癸丑|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Guichuu|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Guichuu|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Water Ox|qq=}}. In the context of {{ill|Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|ja|陰陽五行思想|1=Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|lt=Yin Yang Five Elements|lt_ja=陰陽五行|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin Yang Five Elements Thought|13=User:Immanuelle/Yin-Yang and Wuxing Theory|qq=}}, the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Heavenly Stems]] symbol {{ill|Ren|ja|壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|lt=Mizunoe (壬)|2=ja|3=壬|4=zh|5=壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ren|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoe (壬)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ren|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoe (壬)|qq=}} represents yang [[:en:Water (wuxing)|lt=Water (水)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Water (wuxing)|2=uk|3=Вода (У-сін)|4=als|5=Wasser in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|6=bcl|7=Tubig (wuxing)|8=vi|9=Thủy (Ngũ hành)|10=pt|11=Água (astrologia)|lt=Water (水)|Water (水)]], while the [[:en:Earthly Branches|Earthly Branches]] symbol [[:en:Rat (zodiac)|Rat]] represents yang [[:en:Water (wuxing)|lt=Water (水)|comment=doing this to prevent wrong interwiki linking by bot|1=Water (wuxing)|2=uk|3=Вода (У-сін)|4=als|5=Wasser in dr chinesische Fümf-Elemänt-Leer|6=bcl|7=Tubig (wuxing)|8=vi|9=Thủy (Ngũ hành)|10=pt|11=Água (astrologia)|lt=Water (水)|Water (水)]], resulting in a harmonious relationship ({{ill|Hiwa|ja|比和|1=Wuxing (Chinese philosophy)#Harmonious Relationship (比和)|2=ja|3=五行思想#比和（ひわ）|1=比和|1=Wuxing (Chinese philosophy)#Harmonious Relationship (比和)|2=ja|3=五行思想#比和（ひわ）|lt=Harmonious Relationship (Five Elements)|qq=Harmonious Relationship (Five Elements)|4=el|5=Ου Σιν|lt=Hiwa|lt_ja=比和|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hiwa|13=User:Immanuelle/Wuxing (Chinese philosophy)#Harmonious Relationship (比和)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hiwa|13=User:Immanuelle/Wuxing (Chinese philosophy)#Harmonious Relationship (比和)|qq=}}). ==Pronunciation== * English: Yang Water Rat (壬子) ** Chinese (Mandarin Pinyin): rénzǐ ** Cantonese (Jyutping): jam4 zi2 ** Japanese: ***Kunyomi 1: Mizunoe-ne ***Kunyomi 2: Jinsui-no-ne ***Onyomi 1: jinshi ** Korean (Revised Romanization, Hangul): imja (임자) ** Vietnamese (Hán-Việt): Nhâm Tý
