--> ==Years of Yang Water Rat== A year in the [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] that leaves a remainder of 52 when divided by 60 is a [[:en:Year|year]] of {{ill|Jinshi|ja|1=Yang Water Rat|2=ja|壬子|1=Yang Water Rat|2=ja|3=壬子|4=zh|5=壬子|6=ko|7=임자|lt_ko=임자|8=fr|9=Rat de eau|10=de|11=Wasser-Ratte|12=en|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Water Rat|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jinshi|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jinshi|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Water Rat|qq=}}. {| class="wikitable" |+'''Yang Water Rat (壬子)'s years table''' |- ! [[:en:1st millennium|1st Millennium]] !! [[:en:2nd millennium|2nd Millennium]] !! [[:en:3rd millennium|3rd Millennium]] |- | * [[:en:AD 52|52 AD]] * [[:en:AD 112|112 AD]] * [[:en:172|172 AD]] * [[:en:232|232 AD]] * [[:en:292|292 AD]] * [[:en:352|352 AD]] * [[:en:412|412 AD]] * [[:en:472|472 AD]] * [[:en:532|532 AD]] * [[:en:592|592 AD]] * [[:en:652|652 AD]] * [[:en:712|712 AD]] * [[:en:772|772 AD]] * [[:en:832|832 AD]] * [[:en:892|892 AD]] * [[:en:952|952 AD]] | * [[:en:1012|1012 AD]] * [[:en:1072|1072 AD]] * [[:en:1132|1132 AD]] * [[:en:1192|1192 AD]] * [[:en:1252|1252 AD]] * [[:en:1312|1312 AD]] * [[:en:1372|1372 AD]] * [[:en:1432|1432 AD]] * [[:en:1492|1492 AD]] * [[:en:1552|1552 AD]] * [[:en:1612|1612 AD]] * [[:en:1672|1672 AD]] * [[:en:1732|1732 AD]] * [[:en:1792|1792 AD]] * [[:en:1852|1852 AD]] * [[:en:1912|1912 AD]] * [[:en:1972|1972 AD]] | * {{ill|2032 AD|ja|2032年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2032|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2032 AD|qq=|comment=enwiki is a redirect}} * {{ill|2092 AD|ja|2092年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2092|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2092 AD|qq=|ja_comment=fixed jawiki redirect|3=2090年代|comment=enwiki is a redirect}} * {{ill|2152 AD|ja|2152年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2152|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2152 AD|qq=|ja_comment=fixed jawiki redirect|3=22世紀}} * {{ill|2212 AD|ja|2212年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2212|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2212 AD|qq=|ja_comment=fixed jawiki redirect|3=23世紀}} * {{ill|2272 AD|ja|2272年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2272|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2272 AD|qq=|ja_comment=fixed jawiki redirect|3=23世紀}} * {{ill|2332 AD|ja|2332年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2332|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2332 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2392 AD|ja|2392年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2392|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2392 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2452 AD|ja|2452年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2452|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2452 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2512 AD|ja|2512年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2512|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2512 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2572 AD|ja|2572年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2572|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2572 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2632 AD|ja|2632年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2632|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2632 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2692 AD|ja|2692年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2692|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2692 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2752 AD|ja|2752年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2752|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2752 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2812 AD|ja|2812年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2812|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2812 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2872 AD|ja|2872年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2872|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2872 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2932 AD|ja|2932年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2932|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2932 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} * {{ill|2992 AD|ja|2992年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2992|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2992 AD|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} |}
==Months of Yang Water Rat== Because the water element is duplicated, a superstition arose that while many fires occur in {{ill|Besshi|ja|1=Yang Fire Horse|2=ja|丙午|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Besshi|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Besshi|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Fire Horse|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} years, many water disasters ({{ill|Water disaster|ja|水害|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Water disaster|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Water disaster|qq=}}) occur in {{ill|Jinshi|ja|1=Yang Water Rat|2=ja|壬子|1=Yang Water Rat|2=ja|3=壬子|4=zh|5=壬子|6=ko|7=임자|lt_ko=임자|8=fr|9=Rat de eau|10=de|11=Wasser-Ratte|12=en|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Water Rat|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jinshi|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jinshi|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Water Rat|qq=}} years. In the late Edo period, [[:en:Takizawa Bakin|Kyokutei Bakin]] remarked, "If it is so with a Besshi year, then in a Jinshi year the double presence of water elements will surely bring about a great flood."
However, the superstition that "men born in a Jinshi year have weak constitutions" did not spread; for instance, in [[:en:1972|1972 AD]] (Shōwa 47), nearly 2 million births occurred during a Jinshi year as part of the second [[:en:Baby boom|Baby Boom]], and there are no recorded instances from [[:en:1852|1852 AD]] (Kaei 5) or [[:en:1912|1912 AD]] (Meiji 45/Taishō 1) of men being unable to marry due to being born in a Jinshi year.
==Days of Yang Water Rat== In a [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] year whose final digit is 2 or 7 (when the [[:en:Heavenly Stems|Heavenly Stems]] are {{ill|Ren|ja|壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|lt=Mizunoe (壬)|2=ja|3=壬|4=zh|5=壬|1=Mizunoe (壬)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ren|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoe (壬)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ren|13=User:Immanuelle/Mizunoe (壬)|qq=}} or {{ill|Tei|ja|丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|lt=Hinoto (丁)|2=ja|3=丁|4=zh|5=丁|1=Hinoto (丁)|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tei|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoto (丁)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tei|13=User:Immanuelle/Hinoto (丁)|qq=}}), the month of [[:en:November|November]] is designated as the [[:en:Month|Month]] of {{ill|Jinshi|ja|1=Yang Water Rat|2=ja|壬子|1=Yang Water Rat|2=ja|3=壬子|4=zh|5=壬子|6=ko|7=임자|lt_ko=임자|8=fr|9=Rat de eau|10=de|11=Wasser-Ratte|12=en|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Water Rat|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jinshi|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jinshi|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Water Rat|qq=}}. However, here the term "month" may refer either to the month of the {{ill|Lunisolar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Lunisolar|13=User:Immanuelle/Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=}} or to the [[:en:Solar term|Solar term]] (from [[:en:Daxue (solar term)|Heavy Snow]] until the day before [[:en:Xiaohan|Lesser Cold]]) as applicable.
==Yang Water Rat (壬子)'s Days== ==={{nihongo|selection days|選日|senjitsu|qq=}}=== The selected day for {{ill|Jinshi|ja|1=Yang Water Rat|2=ja|壬子|1=Yang Water Rat|2=ja|3=壬子|4=zh|5=壬子|6=ko|7=임자|lt_ko=임자|8=fr|9=Rat de eau|10=de|11=Wasser-Ratte|12=en|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Water Rat|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jinshi|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jinshi|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Water Rat|qq=}} is the 1st day of {{ill|Hassen|ja|八専|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hassen|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hassen|qq=}}.
