(astrologia)|lt=Water (水)|Water (水)]], resulting in a harmonious relationship ({{ill|Hiwa|ja|比和|1=Wu Xing|2=ja|3=五行思想#比和（ひわ）|1=比和|1=Wuxing (Chinese philosophy)#Harmonious Relationship (比和)|2=ja|3=五行思想#比和（ひわ）|lt=Harmonious Relationship (Five Elements)|qq=Harmonious Relationship (Five Elements)|4=el|5=Ου Σιν|lt=Hiwa|lt_ja=比和|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hiwa|13=User:Immanuelle/Wuxing (Chinese philosophy)#Harmonious Relationship (比和)|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Hiwa|13=User:Immanuelle/Wuxing (Chinese philosophy)#Harmonious Relationship (比和)|qq=|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q218652}}). ==Pronunciation== * English: Yang Water Rat (壬子) ** Chinese (Mandarin Pinyin): rénzǐ ** Cantonese (Jyutping): jam4 zi2 ** Japanese: ***Kunyomi 1: Mizunoe-ne ***Kunyomi 2: Jinsui-no-ne ***Onyomi 1: jinshi ** Korean (Revised Romanization, Hangul): imja (임자) ** Vietnamese (Hán-Việt): Nhâm Tý
