--> ==Years of Yang Water Rat== A year in the [[:en:Common Era|Common Era]] that leaves a remainder of 52 when divided by 60 is a [[:en:Year|year]] of {{ill|Jinshi|ja|1=Yang Water Rat|2=ja|壬子|1=Yang Water Rat|2=ja|3=壬子|4=zh|5=壬子|6=ko|7=임자|lt_ko=임자|8=fr|9=Rat de eau|10=de|11=Wasser-Ratte|12=en|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Water Rat|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jinshi|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Jinshi|13=User:Immanuelle/Yang Water Rat|qq=}}. {| class="wikitable" |+'''Yang Water Rat (壬子)'s years table''' |- ! [[:en:1st millennium|1st Millennium]] !! [[:en:2nd millennium|2nd Millennium]] !! [[:en:3rd millennium|3rd Millennium]] |- | * [[:en:AD 52|52 AD]] * [[:en:AD 112|112 AD]] * [[:en:172|172 AD]] * [[:en:232|232 AD]] * [[:en:292|292 AD]] * [[:en:352|352 AD]] * [[:en:412|412 AD]] * [[:en:472|472 AD]] * [[:en:532|532 AD]] * [[:en:592|592 AD]] * [[:en:652|652 AD]] * [[:en:712|712 AD]] * [[:en:772|772 AD]] * [[:en:832|832 AD]] * [[:en:892|892 AD]] * [[:en:952|952 AD]] | * [[:en:1012|1012 AD]] * [[:en:1072|1072 AD]] * [[:en:1132|1132 AD]] * [[:en:1192|1192 AD]] * [[:en:1252|1252 AD]] * [[:en:1312|1312 AD]] * [[:en:1372|1372 AD]] * [[:en:1432|1432 AD]] * [[:en:1492|1492 AD]] * [[:en:1552|1552 AD]] * [[:en:1612|1612 AD]] * [[:en:1672|1672 AD]] * [[:en:1732|1732 AD]] * [[:en:1792|1792 AD]] * [[:en:1852|1852 AD]] * [[:en:1912|1912 AD]] * [[:en:1972|1972 AD]] | * {{ill|2032 AD|ja|2032年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2032|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2032 AD|qq=|comment=enwiki is a redirect}} * {{ill|2092 AD|ja|2092年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2092|comment=likely broken Sexagenary year|lt=2092 AD|qq=|ja_comment=fixed jawiki redirect|3=2090年代|comment=enwiki is a redirect}} * {{ill|2152 AD|ja|2152年|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/2152|comment=changed title based on wikidata|lt=2152 AD|qq=|ja_comment=fixed jawiki redirect|3=22世紀|1=22nd century|WD=Q11177}} * {{ill